quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,Qayamat ki ghadi kareeb aa gayi aur chaand phatt (split) gaya
  54,2,Magar in logon ka haal yeh hai ke khwa koi nishani dekh lein mooh moadh jaatey hain aur kehte hain yeh to chalta hua jaadu hai
  54,3,Inhon ne (isko bhi) jhutla diya aur apni khwahishat-e-nafs hi ki pairwi ki.Har maamlay ko Aakhir-e-kaar ek anjaam par pahunch kar rehna hai
  54,4,In logon ke saamne (pichle qaumon ke) woh halaat aa chuke hain jinmein sarkashi se baaz rakhne ke liye kafi samaan-e-ibrat hai
  54,5,Aur aisi hikmat jo nasihat ke maqsad ko ba-darja-e-atam (consummate wisdom) pura karti hain magar tambihat(warnings) in par kaargar nahin hoti
  54,6,"Pas aey Nabi, insey rukh pher lo. Jis roz pukarne wala ek sakht nagawaar cheez ki taraf pukarega"
  54,7,Log sehmi hui (down-cast) nigaahon ke saath apni qabraon se is tarah niklenge goya woh bikhri huyi tiddiyan (locusts) hain
  54,8,Pukarne wale ki taraf daudey jaa rahey hongey Aur wahi munkireen (jo duniya mein iska inkar karte thay)us waqt kahenge ke yeh din to bada kathin hai
  54,9,"Insey pehle Nooh ki qaum jhutla chuki hai. Unhon ne hamare bandey ko jhoota karar diya aur kaha ke yeh deewana hai, aur woh buri tarah jhidka (rebuffed) gaya"
  54,10,"Aakhir-e-kaar usne apne Rubb ko pukara ke “main magloob ho chuka , ab tu inse inteqam le”"
  54,11,Tab humne mausla-dhaar baarish se aasmaan ke darwaze khol diye aur zameen ko phaad kar chasmon mein tabdeel kar diya
  54,12,Aur yeh saara paani us kaam ko pura karne ke liye mil gaya jo mukaddar ho chuka tha
  54,13,Aur Nooh ko humne ek takhaton(planks) aur keelon (nails) wali par sawar kar diya
  54,14,Jo hamari nigrani mein chal rahi thi .yeh tha badla us shaks ki khatir jiski na-qadri ki gayi thi
  54,15,"Us kashti ko humne ek nishani bana kar chodh diya, phir koi hai nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,16,"Dekhlo, kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambihaat (warnings)"
  54,17,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,18,"Aad ne jhutlaya, to dekhlo ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambihaat (warnings)"
  54,19,Humne ek paiham nahusat (unremitting misfortune) ke din sakht toofani hawa unpar bhej di jo logon ko utha utha kar is tarah phenk rahi thi
  54,20,Jaise woh jadd (roots) se ukhade huey khajoor ke taney (trunks) hon
  54,21,Pas dekhlo ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambihaat (warnings)
  54,22,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"